caption: b'#Thanksgiving2020 will probably look a little different this year. We\xe2\x80\x99re proud to build the technology that keeps you connected to your loved ones today and every day. Happy Thanksgiving from #TeamQualcomm.'
b'How it started vs. how it\xe2\x80\x99s going. #SnapdragonSummit'
b'Demos by day and dreamy sunsets by night. Throwback to #SnapdragonSummit 2019.'

b'Mark your :spiral_calendar:. We\xe2\x80\x99re livestreaming the keynotes from our 5th annual #SnapdragonSummit on December 1st and 2nd at 7:00am PT. Follow updates on our website at www.qualcomm.com/snapdragonsummit'

b'\xe2\x80\x9cThe 5G Economy in a Post-COVID-19 Era\xe2\x80\x9d is IHS Markit\xe2\x80\x99s latest economic report on #5G. Here are some key highlights about the economic benefits 5G will yield in a post-pandemic world.'

b'Daylight savings has us like :sleeping_face: This sleepy fox was captured on a #Snapdragon 865-powered @xiaomi.usa Mi 10 Pro. #ShotOnSnapdragon :fox_face:'

b'Check out this underwater shipwreck, now home to hundreds of fish and sea creatures. :tropical_fish::spiral_shell: These spooky (but cool) shots were captured in extreme detail on a #Snapdragon 865-powered @samsungmobile Galaxy S20+ #5G. #ShotOnSnapdragon'

b'Here\xe2\x80\x99s what a day at Qualcomm Wireless Academy looks like. Our engineers are teaching virtual courses to help build your knowledge of #5G cellular tech, whether you\xe2\x80\x99re a beginner or a 5G aficionado. Head to qualcommwirelessacademy.com to learn more.'

b'Take in the majesty of Meili Snow Mountain National Park captured in perfect detail on a #Snapdragon 865-powered @xiaomi.usa Mi 10 Pro. #ShotOnSnapdragon'

b'#TBT to when @sdccu Stadium was actually #QualcommStadium. If you didn\xe2\x80\x99t know, this beloved San Diego staple is set to be knocked down next month. While we\xe2\x80\x99re sad to say goodbye, we\xe2\x80\x99ll remember it fondly. Swipe through for some nostalgia.'

b'The brand new OnePlus 8T brings blazing #5G and #WiFi 6 thanks to the #Snapdragon 865 5G Mobile Platform and the Snapdragon X55 5G Modem-RF System. Get ready for next-level power and performance on this amazing phone. #OnePlus8T'

b'Find yourself someone who looks at you the way this Yunnan snub-nosed monkey looks at these leaves. This moment was captured on a #Snapdragon 865-powered @xiaomi.usa Mi 10 Pro in Tachengzen, China. #ShotOnSnapdragon'

b'Not used to seeing these kinds of devices in your feed? We don\xe2\x80\x99t build phones anymore, and now focus on what\xe2\x80\x99s inside them, but today\xe2\x80\x99s #TBT features some Qualcomm classics from back in the day. Can you guess what phones these are?'

b'New from @google: the blazing #Pixel5 and #Pixel4a5G, powered by the #Snapdragon 765G #5G Mobile Platform.'
